msgid "Create custom skills with specific instructions"
msgstr "创建具有特定指令的自定义技能"

#: ../../usage/features.md:74 6e36878c4b444e0aaf311eff6056e45f
msgid "Configure which tools a skill can access"
msgstr "配置技能可以访问的工具"

#: ../../usage/features.md:75 9313ed9140394d009eb8c839ca3dfd58
