#: ../../usage/features.md:87 cdc2a602efbb4f038865f7d9beb58cef
msgid ""
"Custom endpoints are supported via `OPENAI_BASE_URL` and "
"`ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL` for third-party providers."
msgstr "通过 `OPENAI_BASE_URL` 和 `ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL` 支持第三方提供商的自定义端点。"

#: ../../usage/features.md:89 ac0f9b45e86e48d793ea6dcc3eb4cc6f
